{"tid":1559464,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"關於香港國歌，我有野想講","createTime":"2019-09-10T23:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T03:24:22.000Z","uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"56e63f5868f054c98d301bccc9ee60fb28c7064c","tid":1559464,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:30:03.000Z","msg":"我覺得首歌改錯名，歌詞亦唔應該表達「榮光歸香港」<br />\n<br />\n因為聖經有句說話：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Glory to God in the highest</span></strong>, and on earth peace, good will toward men.<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">在至高之處榮耀歸與神！</span>在地上平安歸與他所喜悅的人！<br />\n- 路加福音 2 章 14 節<br />\n<br />\n首歌可能會引起基督徒反感，建議大家改歌名為《願平安歸香港》"},{"pid":"1f382b223efd678831fb0da7b689e2d80fbb3e85","tid":1559464,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GiW8u64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiW8u64.jpg&h=6e2a8a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558977</a>"},{"pid":"ce743b20b4c4e1bb4df612b634e0cfe6ecdad074","tid":1559464,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:36:01.000Z","msg":"畀負評可否發表下意見？"},{"pid":"5dd14e81b01aa8932bcee7b9a098ce08ad3f07a2","tid":1559464,"uid":289041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:43:18.000Z","msg":"願平安 個名好老土"},{"pid":"eb305762818e5d7247d26501c0e31b29e55eb935","tid":1559464,"uid":265932,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"56e63f5868f054c98d301bccc9ee60fb28c7064c","tid":1559464,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:30:03.000Z","msg":"我覺得首歌改錯名，歌詞亦唔應該表達「榮光歸香港」<br />\n<br />\n因為聖經有句說話：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Glory to God in the highest</span></strong>, and on earth peace, good will toward men.<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">在至高之處榮耀歸與神！</span>在地上平安歸與他所喜悅的人！<br />\n- 路加福音 2 章 14 節<br />\n<br />\n首歌可能會引起基督徒反感，建議大家改歌名為《願平安歸香港》"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:07:24.000Z","msg":"首先作首歌內容冇聖經背景，唔需迎合基督徒，唔係為基督徒而作。<br />\n<br />\n其次，首歌唔係代表基督徒，亦未有共識算係國歌，冇話應唔應該呢個說法。<br />\n<br />\n最後，身為基督徒嘅話應該喺自己教會有好多詩歌可以唱，何必執著聖經兩個字，擁護世俗事呢？<br />\n<br />\n如果以基督徒會反感為理由，咁好多歌都令基督徒反感了，因為作曲人根本冇聖經知識，完全根據個人精神，主張人嘅智慧而唔係耶和華嘅智慧。<br />\n<br />\n樓主如果係基督徒嘅話就要小心了。<br />\n魔鬼撒但想用世俗的娛樂，引誘耶和華僕人陷入世俗的網羅，還是專注於屬靈事物吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141f07c1af5969f9c8a1dfa5d7c14d46d3d95651","tid":1559464,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:07:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Glory_to_Ukraine\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FGlory_to_Ukraine&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRegX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=1826d4bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Glory_to_Ukraine</a><br />\n麻煩叫烏克蘭改埋 唔該"},{"pid":"8394e215d8f95ea21e4c55107c42a3c4053a07cb","tid":1559464,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb305762818e5d7247d26501c0e31b29e55eb935","tid":1559464,"uid":265932,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"56e63f5868f054c98d301bccc9ee60fb28c7064c","tid":1559464,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:30:03.000Z","msg":"我覺得首歌改錯名，歌詞亦唔應該表達「榮光歸香港」<br />\n<br />\n因為聖經有句說話：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Glory to God in the highest</span></strong>, and on earth peace, good will toward men.<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">在至高之處榮耀歸與神！</span>在地上平安歸與他所喜悅的人！<br />\n- 路加福音 2 章 14 節<br />\n<br />\n首歌可能會引起基督徒反感，建議大家改歌名為《願平安歸香港》"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:07:24.000Z","msg":"首先作首歌內容冇聖經背景，唔需迎合基督徒，唔係為基督徒而作。<br />\n<br />\n其次，首歌唔係代表基督徒，亦未有共識算係國歌，冇話應唔應該呢個說法。<br />\n<br />\n最後，身為基督徒嘅話應該喺自己教會有好多詩歌可以唱，何必執著聖經兩個字，擁護世俗事呢？<br />\n<br />\n如果以基督徒會反感為理由，咁好多歌都令基督徒反感了，因為作曲人根本冇聖經知識，完全根據個人精神，主張人嘅智慧而唔係耶和華嘅智慧。<br />\n<br />\n樓主如果係基督徒嘅話就要小心了。<br />\n魔鬼撒但想用世俗的娛樂，引誘耶和華僕人陷入世俗的網羅，還是專注於屬靈事物吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:30:02.000Z","msg":"首先我係以香港人既身黎講呢件事<br />\n<br />\n香港有40萬基督徒，佢哋有一定既影響力，擔心佢地會反感都係正常<br />\n<br />\n再者，作為香港人，對國歌發表意見有咩問題？香港我都有份<br />\n<br />\n最後，連登共識係：呢首歌係香港既國歌。點解你話唔係呢？"},{"pid":"7fd33098395772612929e5634f4c681606f62ca1","tid":1559464,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:30:10.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>914</strong></span></span><br />\n天水圍親子遊行<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>915</strong></span></span><br />\n民陣大遊行</div>"},{"pid":"ba9ccf17b63b3672ba3a3edc6c710587e6504fb2","tid":1559464,"uid":121409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:32:23.000Z","msg":"人地原作個po:<br />\n<br />\n榮光: 榮譽;光彩<br />\n<br />\n唐 李白 《大獵賦》：&ldquo;方將延榮光於后昆，軼玄風於邃古。&rdquo; 王琦 注：&ldquo;榮，榮名也。光，光華也。&rdquo; 魯迅 《熱風&middot;隨感錄三十八》：&ldquo;他們的國粹，既然這樣有榮光，他們自然也有榮光了！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4807c0a562fcf56eb9b9376d9e3c3b95a68db9e","tid":1559464,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:32:36.000Z","msg":"屌奶星你班耶撚真係屌少陣就現形"},{"pid":"a7cfb467e04519582ab18052e9b5832a7d9aadb6","tid":1559464,"uid":310495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:37:49.000Z","msg":"咁都有意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e726ba38fe50982bf18edb4b7a50d56c906f101","tid":1559464,"uid":56227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:37:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span s